Author: gcharang#6833
Content:
@KomodoWorld thanks for the feedback, will ask the dev to make the description better

yes, with the available options in "clusters" section currently, the modules will be enabled in every smartchain created

but there won't be 13 modules available, but about 9

```
dilithium, rogue, sudoku, musig
```
are dynamic modules and they require custom compilation of the daemon based on selection, so they aren't available in the composer yet

even among the static modules there is a way to pick and choose which of the modules are enabled, but that too isn't enabled yet
